{"id":363725657,"lang":"python","time":"1Â year","timestamp":1594193224,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"2804 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/363725657/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"3Sum","memory":"16.5 MB","code":"from collections import defaultdict\nclass Solution:\n    def threeSum(self, nums):\n        ans_set = set()\n        nums = sorted(nums)\n        N = len(nums)\n        val2idx = defaultdict(list)\n        for idx, val in enumerate(nums):\n            val2idx[val].append(idx)\n        for i in range(N):\n            for j in range(i+1, N):\n                target = -nums[i] - nums[j]\n                if (target in val2idx) and (j < val2idx[target][-1]):\n                    k = val2idx[target][-1]\n                    ans_set.add((nums[i], nums[j], nums[k]))\n        return ans_set\n        ","compare_result":"","title_slug":"3sum"}
